# 70_whitelist.cf - address and domain whitelist
# Heavily weight known-good senders to prevent false positives.
# This file is split into researched banks, government sites, popular
# Turkish services, and global trusted services.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Research notes
# Bank list sourced from the Banks Association of Turkey (TBB) and
# Participation Banks Association of Turkey (TKBB) data as of June 2025.
# Wikipedia: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_banks_in_Turkey
# Government and popular domains verified from public sites.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
